20-3-24
HINDI Story:

Garmi me himayu bimar pr gaya tha. tb unko aagra laya gya tha. lekin ved bhi kuchh n kar ska. woh gambhi rup se bimar ho gye the. tb ek sadhu ne babar ko kaha tha. agar aap apne sabse kimti cheej bhagwan ko denge toh aapke putra ka jeevan surakshit rhega. putra ko bachane ke liye babar ne khud ka jeevan dene ka pratigya kiya tha. phir babar ka maut ho gya aur himayu susta ho gya tha.

गर्मी मे हिमेउ बिमार प्र गय थ । त्ब उन्को आग्र लय ज्ञ थ । लेकिन वेद भि कुछ न कर स्क । वोह गम्भी रुप से बिमार हो ज्ञे थे । त्ब एक सधु ने बाबार को कहाँ थ । अगर आप अप्ने सब्से किम्ती चीज भग्वान को देङे तोह आप्के पुत्र क जीवन सुरक्षित र्हेग । पुत्र को बचने के लिए बाबार ने खुद क जीवन देने क प्रतिज्ञ किय थ । फिर बाबार क मौत हो ज्ञ और हिमेउ सुस्त हो ज्ञ थ । 

ENGLISH Conversion:

Himanyu fell ill in the summer. then he was brought to aagra. but even doctor could not do anything. Eventually, the disease became serious / got critical. Then a saint said to babar if you sacrifice as your most precious things to god then your son's life will be saved. babar promised to sacrifice his life for saving/to save his son. Then babar died and himanyu recovered/cured.




